Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:29.96,0:00:32.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这么多的肉棒淫汁
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:34.89,0:00:37.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好棒的脚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:40.90,0:00:43.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,嘴巴小穴的口交
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:45.97,0:00:48.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,变得这么大
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:49.98,0:00:52.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的嘴巴跟小穴一样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:54.91,0:00:57.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,超舒服的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:58.92,0:01:01.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我其实超喜欢肉棒的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:04.92,0:01:07.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以跟我做爱超棒的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:09.86,0:01:12.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,死也可以吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:13.87,0:01:16.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,超喜欢我的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:18.94,0:01:21.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,可以用你的肉棒汁射在我的脸上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:28.95,0:01:31.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好臭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:31.88,0:01:34.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这么淫荡的的肉棒真臭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:41.89,0:01:44.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想叫我把他舔干净?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:44.96,0:01:47.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的狂妄的肉棒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:47.90,0:01:50.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好臭
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:50.97,0:01:53.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真是拿你没办法的肉棒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:01:53.91,0:01:56.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好臭的肉棒都会卡脏东西
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:01.91,0:02:04.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,给我你的肉棒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:07.92,0:02:10.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好想要
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:10.86,0:02:13.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,插进我的小穴
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:14.86,0:02:16.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好想要
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:16.86,0:02:19.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想要要你的肉棒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:19.93,0:02:22.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把我弄到不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:25.94,0:02:28.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也会让你很舒服的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:30.88,0:02:33.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:33.95,0:02:36.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,多看我    完全不够
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:37.95,0:02:40.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看到小穴自己会张开的程度
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:43.96,0:02:46.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也会一直一直看你的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:53.97,0:02:56.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喜欢我吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:58.90,0:03:01.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我超喜欢你的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:03.98,0:03:06.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喜欢我吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:07.98,0:03:10.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说喜欢我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:10.92,0:03:13.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喜欢你超喜欢你的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:17.86,0:03:20.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我觉得
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:22.93,0:03:25.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,果然比起钱更喜欢肉棒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:29.87,0:03:32.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,因为肉棒很舒服
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:36.94,0:03:39.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肉棒看起来都很幸福
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:44.95,0:03:47.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一插进去肉棒都很幸福
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:51.89,0:03:54.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:54.96,0:03:57.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,战争也会不见的不是吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:01.90,0:04:04.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,小穴跟肉棒可以拯救世界
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:08.97,0:04:11.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不能去风俗区
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:15.91,0:04:18.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看就会很舒服的事情知道吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:23.92,0:04:26.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,风俗女都只看你的脸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:33.93,0:04:36.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会一直看着你的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:39.94,0:04:42.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看着看着
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:42.88,0:04:45.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,变态是称赞的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:50.88,0:04:53.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以给我看你淫荡的脸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:10.90,0:05:13.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,从现在弄到你头脑空白的状态让你舒服
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:21.98,0:05:24.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,别客气     请尽情爽
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:29.86,0:05:32.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会带你上天堂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:51.88,0:05:54.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么都没做就已经勃起了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:58.95,0:06:01.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在想象吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:03.89,0:06:06.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在想象我吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:11.90,0:06:14.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在想象让我帮你舒服吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:17.90,0:06:20.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也太快了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:24.98,0:06:27.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:28.98,0:06:31.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,拿你没办法的肉棒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:37.92,0:06:40.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,碰到我没法
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:47.93,0:06:50.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还没碰就这样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:53.94,0:06:56.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,臭肉棒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:57.94,0:07:00.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想让我摸吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:04.88,0:07:07.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真没办法一直动
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:12.89,0:07:15.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不用碰也会射吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:20.90,0:07:23.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不碰好吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:28.91,0:07:34.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,还没碰都勃起了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:40.92,0:07:43.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想被碰的话求我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:45.86,0:07:45.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:53.87,0:07:56.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不求我的话不摸喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:59.87,0:08:02.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,再大声点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:08.95,0:08:11.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,求求看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:11.88,0:08:14.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,淫荡的肉棒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:18.96,0:08:21.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快说求你拜托碰我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:30.97,0:08:33.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快求
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:35.91,0:08:38.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想被弄对吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:40.98,0:08:43.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我来摸你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:05.94,0:09:08.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,血管超凸的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:11.94,0:09:14.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这会爆掉吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:16.88,0:09:19.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,淫荡的肉棒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:23.96,0:09:26.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已经娈超硬的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:27.96,0:09:30.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好厉害
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:34.90,0:09:37.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,手指感觉到你的震动
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:45.98,0:09:48.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,超热的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:48.91,0:09:51.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,一直动
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:52.92,0:09:55.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的手指超热的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:58.92,0:10:01.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这样就够了吗?满足了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:08.93,0:10:11.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,会让你很舒服的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:21.88,0:10:24.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这个超舒服的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:30.96,0:10:33.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你也有用过吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:39.90,0:10:42.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:46.97,0:10:49.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,超湿的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:50.98,0:10:53.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,超色的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:57.92,0:10:59.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你看这个
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:59.92,0:11:02.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,湿到不行
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:09.93,0:11:12.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的小穴也超湿的喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:14.87,0:11:17.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:17.94,0:11:20.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,湿答答的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:21.94,0:11:24.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:24.88,0:11:27.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你也很喜欢对吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:32.89,0:11:35.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的小穴也变成这样了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:39.96,0:11:42.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,超湿的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:43.96,0:11:46.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的小穴湿透了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:56.91,0:11:59.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听得到吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:00.91,0:12:03.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,色色的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:03.98,0:12:06.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你看
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:06.92,0:12:09.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听不到吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:09.86,0:12:12.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的小穴超淫荡的喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:14.93,0:12:17.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,湿答答的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:18.93,0:12:21.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也想这么舒服吧?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:23.87,0:12:26.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想被插吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:30.94,0:12:33.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我来帮你楼
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:43.89,0:12:46.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的手如何?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:48.96,0:12:51.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,湿答答的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:54.97,0:12:57.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,超想要的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:00.97,0:13:03.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的手超紧的吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:04.98,0:13:07.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,淫荡的肉棒湿答答的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:15.92,0:13:18.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好厉害
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:18.86,0:13:21.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肉棒都边的这么硬
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:24.86,0:13:27.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,淫荡的肉棒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:28.87,0:13:31.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,湿答答的   黏黏的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:40.88,0:13:43.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你看好厉害
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:43.95,0:13:46.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你看好热
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:51.96,0:13:54.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,听得到吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:54.89,0:13:57.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的肉棒变得超热的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:59.97,0:14:02.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,就像石头一样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:02.90,0:14:05.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的龟头超硬的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:06.91,0:14:09.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的手这么舒服吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:09.98,0:14:12.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,真色
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:13.98,0:14:16.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好厉害
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:26.93,0:14:29.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的手让你这么湿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:33.87,0:14:36.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,湿答答的文硬硬的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:39.87,0:14:42.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的肉棒被我强奸了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:46.95,0:14:49.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想干嘛就干嘛耶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:52.95,0:14:55.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,知道吗?在这世界有好肉棒跟坏肉棒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:05.90,0:15:08.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好肉棒就像你这个又硬又粗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:18.98,0:15:21.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,超喜欢的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:24.98,0:15:27.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,超喜欢淫荡的肉棒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:31.92,0:15:34.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喜欢肉棒超喜欢肉棒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:37.93,0:15:40.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我会变得很奇怪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:40.87,0:15:43.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,超喜欢肉棒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:43.94,0:15:46.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我超喜欢肉棒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:47.94,0:15:50.88,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,想一直摸下去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:50.88,0:15:53.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么这么舒服
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:56.88,0:15:59.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,为什么你有这么棒的肉棒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:02.89,0:16:05.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,舒服吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:06.89,0:16:09.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,这肉棒看起来好舒服
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:12.90,0:16:15.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,超喜欢肉棒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:15.97,0:16:18.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喜欢我吗?告诉我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:21.97,0:16:24.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,说你喜欢我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:26.91,0:16:29.98,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我超喜欢你的肉棒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:30.92,0:16:33.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,超爱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:33.99,0:16:36.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你看变得这么硬
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:37.86,0:16:40.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,舒服吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:42.93,0:16:45.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,湿答答的肉棒也超喜欢你的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:48.93,0:16:51.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全都爱你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:55.87,0:16:58.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全力的爱你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:04.95,0:17:07.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,全力爱你的肉棒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:10.96,0:17:13.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,已经娈得这么硬了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:13.89,0:17:16.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我超开心的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:19.90,0:17:22.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,舒服吗?开心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:22.97,0:17:24.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好舒服
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:24.97,0:17:27.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的手舒服吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:32.98,0:17:35.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,变得这么硬
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:38.98,0:17:41.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肉棒在说想射
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:42.19,0:17:42.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:42.86,0:17:45.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肉棒在说想射喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:45.92,0:17:48.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,硬到快撑不住了喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:53.93,0:17:56.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快射了吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:57.94,0:17:59.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肉棒快裂掉了
