Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:15.95,0:18:18.89,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快说阿淫荡的肉棒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:20.89,0:18:22.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,淫荡的肉棒快说喜欢我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:22.90,0:18:25.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快说啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:26.90,0:18:29.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喜欢吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:30.90,0:18:32.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,快说啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:32.91,0:18:35.97,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,肉棒快裂掉了喔
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:37.98,0:18:40.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,喜欢吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:44.92,0:18:47.99,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,淫荡的肉棒
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:48.92,0:18:51.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,硬硬的这肉棒怎么了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:54.93,0:18:57.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,超色的
