Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:53.87,0:27:56.94,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了吗?想被捏吗?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:27:56.94,0:27:59.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比我还敏感   像女生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:21.89,0:28:24.96,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好吃这边也
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:36.98,0:28:39.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好湿
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:46.99,0:28:49.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好敏感
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:28:59.93,0:29:02.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好硬   一直抖
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:05.94,0:29:08.87,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,怎么了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:12.88,0:29:15.95,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好硬
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:27.96,0:29:30.90,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,看好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:45.98,0:29:48.91,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好厉害
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:50.92,0:29:52.92,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,硬硬的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:52.92,0:29:55.85,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下一个想被弄哪?
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:29:56.92,0:29:59.86,Default,NTP,0,0,0,,下一个
